										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1641112473786 wd-rs-61d1638cccd65"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>Sometimes and it&#8217;s rare in the WooCommerce checkout page to show a &#8220;Spinner&#8221; on the Review Order section. It happens when something goes wrong &#8211; In order to fix the issue you may need to checkÂ <strong>WooCommerce &gt; System Status</strong>Â for errors â€“ often errors will be highlighted.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Still, having problems? Common causes and resolutions are listed below <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/1f447.png" alt="ðŸ‘‡" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>

		</div>
	</div>
<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1641112963150 vc_row-has-fill wd-rs-61d1657ccd4a5"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">		
		<div id="wd-61d1656e623e0" class="title-wrapper wd-wpb set-mb-s reset-last-child  wd-rs-61d1656e623e0 wd-title-color-primary wd-underline-colored wd-title-style-default wd-width-100 text-left ">
			
			<div class="liner-continer">
				<h4 class="woodmart-title-container title  wd-font-weight-600 wd-fontsize-xl" >Fix#1 Transactional Emails causing trouble</h4>
							</div>
			
			
			
		</div>
		
		
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>You can enable the following filter to defer emails from sending until after the order is sent through, which speeds things up:</p>
<p>add_filter( &#8216;woocommerce_defer_transactional_emails&#8217;, &#8216;__return_true&#8217; );</p>

		</div>
	</div>
</div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1641113398366 vc_row-has-fill wd-rs-61d167300343c"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">		
		<div id="wd-61d165e95ecb0" class="title-wrapper wd-wpb set-mb-s reset-last-child  wd-rs-61d165e95ecb0 wd-title-color-primary wd-underline-colored wd-title-style-default wd-width-100 text-left ">
			
			<div class="liner-continer">
				<h4 class="woodmart-title-container title  wd-font-weight-600 wd-fontsize-xl" >Fix#2 AJAX error due to WordPress settings.</h4>
							</div>
			
			
			
		</div>
		
		
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>The URLâ€™s inÂ <strong>Settings &gt; General</strong>Â need to match â€“ this is because AJAX requests donâ€™t work across different domains:</p>

		</div>
	</div>

	<div  class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_center">
		
		<figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure">
			<div class="vc_single_image-wrapper vc_box_border  vc_box_border_grey"><img width="2560" height="440" src="./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.46.13-PM-scaled.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-full" alt="" title="Screen Shot 2022-01-02 at 2.46.13 PM" srcset="./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.46.13-PM-scaled.jpg 2560w, ./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.46.13-PM-300x52.jpg 300w, ./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.46.13-PM-1024x176.jpg 1024w, ./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.46.13-PM-768x132.jpg 768w, ./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.46.13-PM-1536x264.jpg 1536w, ./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.46.13-PM-2048x352.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></div>
		</figure>
	</div>
</div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1641113398366 vc_row-has-fill wd-rs-61d167300343c"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">		
		<div id="wd-61d1674fd26b0" class="title-wrapper wd-wpb set-mb-s reset-last-child  wd-rs-61d1674fd26b0 wd-title-color-primary wd-underline-colored wd-title-style-default wd-width-100 text-left ">
			
			<div class="liner-continer">
				<h4 class="woodmart-title-container title  wd-font-weight-600 wd-fontsize-xl" >Fix#3 Other JavaScript errors and conflicts</h4>
							</div>
			
			
			
		</div>
		
		
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>Themes and plugins can often cause problems (especially poorly coded ones!) with JavaScript. To check for errors using your browserâ€™s error console <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/1f447.png" alt="ðŸ‘‡" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>

		</div>
	</div>

	<div  class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_center">
		
		<figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure">
			<div class="vc_single_image-wrapper vc_box_border  vc_box_border_grey"><img width="1749" height="651" src="./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.51.53-PM.png" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-full" alt="" title="Screen Shot 2022-01-02 at 2.51.53 PM" srcset="./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.51.53-PM.png 1749w, ./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.51.53-PM-300x112.png 300w, ./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.51.53-PM-1024x381.png 1024w, ./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.51.53-PM-768x286.png 768w, ./../wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2022-01-02-at-2.51.53-PM-1536x572.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1749px) 100vw, 1749px" /></div>
		</figure>
	</div>
</div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1641113398366 vc_row-has-fill wd-rs-61d167300343c"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">		
		<div id="wd-61d1683d98c18" class="title-wrapper wd-wpb set-mb-s reset-last-child  wd-rs-61d1683d98c18 wd-title-color-primary wd-underline-colored wd-title-style-default wd-width-100 text-left ">
			
			<div class="liner-continer">
				<h4 class="woodmart-title-container title  wd-font-weight-600 wd-fontsize-xl" >Fix#4 WP Memory Limit</h4>
							</div>
			
			
			
		</div>
		
		
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p><strong>Edit your wp-config.php file</strong></p>
<p>Wp-config.php is one of the most important WordPress files because it contains your base configuration details. Youâ€™ll find it in the root of your WordPress file directory. To edit the memory limit and upload limit, look for this line:</p>
<p><code>define('WP_MEMORY_LIMIT', '32M');</code></p>
<p>Modify the second parameter by increasing it. As I mentioned a PHP memory limit of 128M should be more than enough.</p>
<p><code>define('WP_MEMORY_LIMIT', '128M');</code></p>

		</div>
	</div>

